    <item>
      <title>日本将与关西核能公司达成协议，发行下一轮核电融资债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/japan-set-for-next-nuclear-power-funding-bond-with-kansai-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[关西电力公司计划发行日本第二笔过渡债券，为核电项目提供融资，这是日本推动发行在国外不受欢迎但在国内得到政府支持的债券的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/japan-set-for-next-nuclear-power-funding-bond-with-kansai-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 08:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
