      <title>奥地利航空客机在冰雹击碎机头锥体后安全着陆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/austrian-flight-lands-safely-after-hailstones-rip-away-nose-cone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一场猛烈的冰雹摧毁了奥地利航空公司一架飞机的大部分机头，并导致驾驶舱窗户布满裂缝，但飞机最终安全降落在维也纳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/austrian-flight-lands-safely-after-hailstones-rip-away-nose-cone</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 07:17:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Engelhart 收购 Trailstone，扩大电力和天然气交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/engelhart-to-acquire-trailstone-in-clean-energy-transition-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Engelhart Commodities Trading Partners 已同意收购 Trailstone，此交易可能会造就电力交易领域的一家大型企业，因为各大公司纷纷参与动荡的电力市场，而电力市场已成为该行业利润的主要来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/engelhart-to-acquire-trailstone-in-clean-energy-transition-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
